# Phase 27: Pin/Unpin Auto-Hide — Walkthrough

## Summary

Added VS Code-style auto-hide pin functionality to the Library (Songs/Bible) pane. The feature uses a two-state system (pin mode + visibility) with a permanent icon rail on the left side.

