### Key Design Decisions

1. **Permanent Icon Rail**: Always visible on the far left (32px), not just when pane is hidden
2. **Docked vs Overlay**: Pinned mode uses flex-based docking (layout reflows); Auto-hide mode uses Stack-based overlay (no layout shift)
3. **Dismiss Barrier**: In auto-hide mode, a transparent GestureDetector covers the entire area behind the overlay to detect outside clicks

